{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CcVqav9NC9tnmanpLCthEY","type":"tool_result","content":"#   ### Smażona zielona fasolka [real]\n#   Expected: Smażona zielona fasolka\n#   Smażona zielona fasolka\n#   GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\nThe title was on line 1 with no ambiguity, but the extractor returned empty. The likely culprit is the Korean (Hangul) text on line 3 disrupting the extraction pipeline rather than any difficulty identifying the title itself. The fix recommendation: fall back to the first non-blank line when the extractor produces nothing.\n{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\"ona zielona fasolka\\\"\"}},\"session_id\":\"ef859d4a-7bf5-423e-90d6-86c0ac905776\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"629088b3-b22f-41f9-b12b-4a3f447bf70a\"}\n{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\"empty string\"}},\"session_id\":\"ef859d4a-7bf5-423e-90d6-86c0ac905776\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"84ea7e21-5c79-4025-80af-7b7e68c48652\"}\n{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" empty\"}},\"session_id\":\"ef859d4a-7bf5-423e-90d6-86c0ac905776\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"fba0233e-0ef5-462c-9f34-8d4d028d9da9\"}\n{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" title\\n2. \\\"GREEN BEANS\"}},\"session_id\":\"ef859d4a-7bf5-423e-90d6-86c0ac905776\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"36e61884-c820-4653-a110-f3a3ed4fab21\"}\n{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" empty string\"}},\"session_id\":\"ef859d4a-7bf5-423e-90d6-86c0ac905776\",\"parent_tool_use_i